Phase 1: Python Fundamentals:

tep 1: Python Setup
Install Python:

Download and install the latest version of Python from python.org.
Check if Python is installed by opening the terminal or command prompt and typing:
bash
Copy code
"python --version"

Choose a Code Editor:

VS Code: Lightweight and highly customizable (Download VS Code).
PyCharm: More focused on Python development (Download PyCharm).
